  "title": "Retail Store Manager - Assistant (5 Days)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Retail Company</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $4000 - $6000 (basic) + $100 (Transport Allowance) + Attendance Allowance + Commission</strong></li><li><strong>Working hour: 5 Days (9:00am – 7:00am / 1:30pm – 11:30pm)</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Chinatown / Little India</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Support the Store Manager in daily store operations and administration.</li><li>Ensure store cleanliness, visual standards, and inventory availability.</li><li>Drive sales performance and deliver high-quality customer service.</li><li>Supervise, train, and motivate staff; assist with scheduling and attendance.</li><li>Implement promotions and in-store marketing initiatives.</li><li>Prepare sales and operational reports; support budgeting and cost control.</li><li>Resolve operational issues and escalate when necessary to maintain smooth store operations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business, Retail Management, or a related field</li><li>Minimum 2 years retail experience, preferably in a supervisory role</li></ul><p><br />Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
